show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/U8Amkm
show.description: A romantic comedy of errors unfolds when two best friends unknowingly end up dating each other's intended partners after meeting at a hotel, leading to complications when both couples must navigate family expectations, tradition, and love in a wealthy Indian business family. As they fall deeper in love with the "wrong" partners, the truth of their switched identities threatens to unravel everything.
